Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.76,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Every hour of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.06,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}whenever I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.67,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}these impatient feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.19,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}simply overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:52.68,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Even though it's easy to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.90,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}when you stand in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:08:02.04,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}my personality stands up and gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I can usually pull through with my assertiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.38,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that's just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:16.59,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But no matter how hard I try, I can't break the wall that's between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:20.10,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I want you to realise… my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.72,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So I always send a gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:27.64,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}of "I really love you" your way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.77,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}with all of my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.92,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}My flimsy silky heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.24,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}After meeting you, I finally realised
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:43.84,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that I'm really clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.11,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}The scars from love that I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.67,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}have started to ache all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.26,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Someday, like how I normally would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:01.84,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I must say "I love you", or else I'll become even weaker.
