Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will chase after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you go left, I'll go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President, they're running in the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say when I catch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you've always wanted to know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Takasu Ryuuji too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought I should let you have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought to myself, "If Taiga, my best friend, needs him..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was just my arrogance confusing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've underestimated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that my happiness doesn't depend on anyone but me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your happiness doesn't depend on anyone but yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see what you're going to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I tripped while I was running...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it stopped yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were crying for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I would cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... Normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is sort of a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I talked about what I can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's my willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Willpower?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you my brother plays baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to play baseball too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was better than him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't keep playing because I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I plan to save money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then get into a sports university and aim for the national softball league.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll shout out to the whole world:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is the happiness I chose and achieved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because I was obsessive about it, I decided to not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's hard and painful, I've decided I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone sees me go through hardship and pain, and then cry, I guess it's a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that hairpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the present you wanted to give to me on Christmas Eve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I really didn't know at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a present from Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I decided not to take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologise for wearing it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that hairpin right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my room, but{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's something else that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that you like Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Takasu-kun, this is a giant goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run towards the thing that you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ka-su, hey! Ta-ka-su, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ka-su!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an honest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come to work, even though you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, about what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Minorin's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If I want to run away again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our paycheck's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Takasu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, she'll be staying with{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'd stay with you, that man, and that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who doesn't get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you wouldn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you lied and broke that promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fainted because you pushed yourself too much for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm working in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're a family, we should help each other out{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to concentrate on your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find something you want to do and live a good life{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who didn't concentrate on their studies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who couldn't do what they want and failed in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit forcing your failures on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shitty old man's business failed, and he ran away.{damned changed to shitty ("kuso") to keep consitency with previous eps - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he told my real mum to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she already has a new family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's even pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her new husband is tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so their child will definitely have long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... How can I fit in with a family like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, I'd only make everything awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same at the shitty old man's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my presence, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had never been born, Yasuko would definitely have a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still young, so she could probably redo high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults are really selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bring others trouble because of their own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think I might be the one who's troubling Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, if I had never been born{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you pig-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Idiot! Idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy! Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you solve by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say something as naïve as that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what you were saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter who you spend your life with,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be able to see you, Takasu Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't say things like, "If only I had never been born"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really dwell on trivial things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What blood type are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with horoscopes, but roast lamb is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be eighteen in two months!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run away from Yasuko and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run and run,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'll sleep and wake up, and then I'll run until it's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we'll both be adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life will be yours until I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lov{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to listen to what I have to say first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sneaky dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proposing should be left to guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, I made a promise with Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to show her what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then, let's say it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lov{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lov{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is calling at such an important time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going, it's getting cold here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?! It'll be a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Takasu, what the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mum and Aisaka's mum are searching everywhere for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just come to where I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sneezed on my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two all wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we meeting at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mothers haven't come here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My aunt isn't here today, so come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold if you stay in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a shower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this, and this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taiga, your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Yuusaku said he'll bring you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm sorry for bothering you.{mfw the editor thinks anyways is a real word - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You love Taiga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who forced me to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?! How could you?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.58,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you guys planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...plan to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more months, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you supporting them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away, and then getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too fast of a development!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Ryuuji turns eighteen, we'll{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, where will you be living?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay in a business hotel, or maybe even a manga café for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to live like that forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well, after I come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine search parties looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone at school finding out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two might even get expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I want just end up breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to not desire anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my feelings were rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to break this "all the \Nthings I want just end up breaking" jinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my savings that I always hold onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my life savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think your actions are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to approve of them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if this is what you want to do, I have no right to object to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay me back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the key to my villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been there already, so you should know how to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin has some things to discuss with Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why do I have to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're friends again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Stupid Chi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Minorin, Stupid Chi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to discuss with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hand off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so weak that I can't even stand anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to show me your crying face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying is a nosebleed of the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Taiga took Takasu-kun away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I decided to never cry again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trip while running down a hallway, you'll get a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trip in life, you'll cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for us to be talking about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, for ten years, for twenty years, for sixty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,life will go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to run out once you've got your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Ya-chan{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to bring your hair dryer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to carry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring too much light clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out right after you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, call me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your grandparents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them this watch and they'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mirano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called at dawn saying she'll be taking a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll still be a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been showing it off since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it already! Just how long do you plan to show it off for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who said that\Nschool isn't a place for trading chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trading. I'm just bringing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they catch a cold together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like a "fever".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight on! Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oohashi! Fight on! Fight on! Fight on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.23,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to see them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless how strong a will she has,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she broke down after being dumped by both Taiga and Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to have a snowball fight with{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Pure white sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's food for running away, I picked something more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, cigar chocolate, chicken wafers and{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made lunch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you buy lunch from train stations when you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only cares about her own reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll make a big fuss out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about Ya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say it now because we're running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when Ya-chan said we're a family of three,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was truly overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what my "family" is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when we're really becoming a family like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will Ya-chan cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be goodbye forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't want to run away with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your grandchild, Takasu Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not escaping, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji showed me his method of dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at me. Don't get mad at me.
